surf_underearth - By Slasher/Hussa

Combat Surf Map (:

Target: Get to the end, as fast as you can, grab a weapon with a special Effect (Strong Heal M3, normal heal deagle, Lighted Scout .. ), go to jail, and kill some people. (:

Jail Opens regulary, don't worry. No other way out of jail, than the way in the middle, to keep some combat.

The used music in this map is copyrighted by their own producers :b

have fun :bb
